Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.52,0:00:06.19,Kanojo_Flag_Main,B,0000,0000,0000,,She should have gone this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.50,0:00:07.93,Kanojo_Flag_Main,G,0000,0000,0000,,Let's look over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.13,0:00:13.65,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,It seems they've left.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.99,0:00:16.53,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,What did you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.53,0:00:17.24,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Serika,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.24,0:00:18.79,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Serika,0000,0000,0000,,and why do you
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.79,0:00:22.45,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Serika,0000,0000,0000,,think I did something?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.96,0:00:30.86,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Serikyan!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.86,0:00:32.46,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Serika,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, don't say that so loud.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.08,0:00:34.22,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,You know her, Nanami?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.22,0:00:36.43,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,You don't know Serikyan?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.48,0:00:39.64,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,She's an idol on the national stage...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.64,0:00:42.10,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Ginyuuin Serika!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.10,0:00:42.88,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.87,0:00:45.55,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Ginyuuin...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.86,0:00:57.37,Kanojo_Show_Title,Title,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,1)}If {\c&H53AC43&}Her {\c&H085DF0&}Flag {\c&HD2C345&}Breaks
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.03,0:02:21.03,Kanojo_Flag_Ep_Number,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(770,1)\c&HD8C258&}Flag {\c&H2CAEEA&}11
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.03,0:02:21.03,Kanojo_Flag_Ep_Title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(770,1)}We Don't {\c&HDBC55B&}all Have {\c&H48C684&}to Dance. {\c&H984FDF&}I can {\c&H22A3E9&}Dance {\c&HDBC55B&}by Myself
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.53,0:02:24.89,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,She's sold more than 10,000,000 CDs!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.89,0:02:28.05,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Her photos make magazines sell five times better!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.05,0:02:30.21,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,She's constantly on tons \Nof different TV programs.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.61,0:02:34.61,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,In just the last six months she's \Nclimbed to the top of the rankings.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.61,0:02:37.00,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,She's easily the most famous idol right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.00,0:02:39.63,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Her name,0000,0000,0000,,Her name: Serikyan!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.63,0:02:41.01,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, I've never heard of her.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.36,0:02:43.01,Kanojo_Flag_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you stupid?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.01,0:02:44.24,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,You've never heard of Serikyan?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.24,0:02:46.24,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Do you come from another world\Nwhere they don't have TVs?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.24,0:02:48.39,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Do you live with the elves? Are you an elf?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.55,0:02:51.81,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Serika,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I need to work on my popularity.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.81,0:02:53.28,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's fine, Serikyan.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.28,0:02:56.14,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,This guy's an elf and doesn't know anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.14,0:02:56.74,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.82,0:03:04.83,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Serika,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for letting me borrow \Nyour uniform, Nanami-chin.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.83,0:03:07.48,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Serika,0000,0000,0000,,The uniforms are really cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.34,0:03:11.54,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Serikyan in a school uniform is so great.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.58,0:03:15.59,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, if you use that uniform \Nto disguise yourself,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.59,0:03:17.74,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,it should be more difficult \Nfor people to recognize you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.09,0:03:19.47,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Serika,0000,0000,0000,,You know what you're doing, Nanami-chin!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.47,0:03:21.47,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Serika,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give you a hug.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.55,0:03:25.49,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I've never seen this side of Nanami.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.92,0:03:28.35,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I never would have thought \Nyou'd be so into idols.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.15,0:03:30.42,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,I don't like idols.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.42,0:03:31.77,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,I like Serikyan!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.11,0:03:34.96,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,So why is this "Serikyan" here anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.26,0:03:37.66,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,You don't know anything, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.66,0:03:39.27,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,On the last day of the School Fair,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.27,0:03:40.99,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,there's a special Serikyan concert.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.99,0:03:42.30,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,That's obviously why she's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.30,0:03:43.04,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.34,0:03:45.28,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Today isn't the last day.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.52,0:03:48.41,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Serika,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I wanted to take a \Nlook at the stage and such,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.41,0:03:51.79,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Serika,0000,0000,0000,,and you know, have some \Nfun at the fair, maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.79,0:03:55.71,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Well, then, we'll just have to \Nshow you around the fair, then!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.95,0:03:57.79,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Serika,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Nanami-chin!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.09,0:04:00.34,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Serika,0000,0000,0000,,But aren't you on a date with your boyfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.76,0:04:02.48,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,H-He's not my boyfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.48,0:04:04.30,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,You're far more important to me
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.30,0:04:06.69,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,than this dark elf over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.01,0:04:09.20,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Now, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.20,0:04:11.14,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Serika,0000,0000,0000,,Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.57,0:04:19.10,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,The bard from the fairy tale...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.22,0:04:21.96,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I imagine that's her...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.11,0:04:25.88,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,No use in worrying about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.88,0:04:27.98,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I decided that I would have fun while I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.78,0:04:30.12,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.12,0:04:32.02,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.02,0:04:33.41,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,R-Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.89,0:04:55.14,Kanojo_Flag_Main,R,0000,0000,0000,,President!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.43,0:05:04.10,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Serika,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.10,0:05:08.10,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Serika,0000,0000,0000,,How many girls are you leading on?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.10,0:05:10.28,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not really...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.53,0:05:13.47,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Serika,0000,0000,0000,,You were supposed to be on a date \Nat the school fair with Nanami-chin,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.47,0:05:15.25,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Serika,0000,0000,0000,,but now you're flirting \Nwith other girls instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.25,0:05:17.75,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Serika,0000,0000,0000,,I feel bad for Nanami-chin!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.24,0:05:21.44,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't a date. \NIt was more like I forced him,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.44,0:05:24.55,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,but I'm glad you're concerned for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.90,0:05:26.09,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Serikyan!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.09,0:05:27.59,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Serika,0000,0000,0000,,Nanami-chin!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.40,0:05:30.53,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.53,0:05:30.93,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.52,0:05:34.92,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,You wanted to see the stage you'll be \Nperforming on during the last day, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.53,0:05:36.44,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I think that's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.99,0:05:49.78,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,You're a national idol,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.78,0:05:52.02,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,so this might not be much,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.02,0:05:54.79,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,but we're all looking forward \Nto your performance.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.16,0:05:59.29,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Serika,0000,0000,0000,,No, I like these local concerts.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.95,0:06:02.47,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Serika,0000,0000,0000,,The first concert I performed \Nwas at a school fair.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.28,0:06:06.16,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Serika,0000,0000,0000,,A school fair at my middle school...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.16,0:06:07.96,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Serika,0000,0000,0000,,We didn't have a stage,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.96,0:06:10.76,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Serika,0000,0000,0000,,so we just decorated the gym.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.80,0:06:13.47,debut_06:10,Serika,0000,0000,0000,,Ginyuuin Serika Idol Debut
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.70,0:06:16.47,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Serika,0000,0000,0000,,I had just debuted,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.47,0:06:19.25,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Serika,0000,0000,0000,,and couldn't sing because I was so nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.67,0:06:21.73,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Serika,0000,0000,0000,,But my classmates
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.19,0:06:25.19,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Serika,0000,0000,0000,,and my teachers cheered me on.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.19,0:06:27.09,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Serika,0000,0000,0000,,I was so happy I could've cried.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.39,0:06:29.57,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Serika,0000,0000,0000,,They supported me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.76,0:06:31.74,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Serika,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.12,0:06:35.24,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Serika,0000,0000,0000,,For the next year and a half \Nno one even noticed me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.86,0:06:38.75,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Serika,0000,0000,0000,,I was an idol in name only.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.42,0:06:42.43,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Serika,0000,0000,0000,,Talent.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.00,0:06:44.41,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Serika,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I don't have any.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.98,0:06:48.85,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Serika,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I should stop calling myself an idol.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.05,0:06:54.58,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Serika,0000,0000,0000,,I'm supposed to make everyone happy,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.58,0:06:57.59,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Serika,0000,0000,0000,,but instead they made me feel happy,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.59,0:06:59.26,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Serika,0000,0000,0000,,and I couldn't even return the favor...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.08,0:07:03.23,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Serika,0000,0000,0000,,I wish I could do more...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.66,0:07:04.52,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Serika,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.18,0:07:22.54,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,You can't give up here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.85,0:07:23.47,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Serika,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.07,0:07:27.14,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,You will come to inspire people,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.46,0:07:30.15,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,and become a woman that \Nrepresents people's dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.73,0:07:32.73,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Your heart is not yet dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.80,0:07:35.73,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,If you fall, you can get back up,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.73,0:07:37.66,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,provided you don't give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.95,0:07:42.56,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Serika,0000,0000,0000,,I can keep going?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.56,0:07:44.72,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Serika,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think I can fly again?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.12,0:07:48.69,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Serika,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think I can sing and give people hope?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.67,0:07:50.44,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,You can.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.49,0:07:56.92,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,You have a flag on
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.22,0:08:00.13,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,your head that says you'll succeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.22,0:08:06.88,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Serika,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.37,0:08:12.02,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Serika,0000,0000,0000,,Half a year later,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.32,0:08:15.66,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Serika,0000,0000,0000,,Serikyan became a super-idol,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.66,0:08:17.51,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Serika,0000,0000,0000,,and it was all thanks to his words.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.91,0:08:19.86,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Serika,0000,0000,0000,,He said I had a success flag.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.86,0:08:21.18,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Serika,0000,0000,0000,,What a prophet.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.18,0:08:25.06,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Serika,0000,0000,0000,,I call him the purple flag guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.06,0:08:27.73,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Serika,0000,0000,0000,,I never was able to thank him,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.73,0:08:29.43,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Serika,0000,0000,0000,,but I wonder if he's out there somewhere,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.43,0:08:31.05,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Serika,0000,0000,0000,,having heard my songs.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.07,0:08:33.74,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Serika,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I just told you
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.74,0:08:36.71,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Serika,0000,0000,0000,,my secret origin story. Whoops.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.71,0:08:38.06,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Serika,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell anyone,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.06,0:08:41.54,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Serika,0000,0000,0000,,'Kay? 'Kay?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.80,0:08:43.37,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,R-Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.80,0:08:45.97,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Serika,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, I'll be going.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.97,0:08:48.28,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,You're leaving, Serikyan?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.28,0:08:51.09,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Serika,0000,0000,0000,,Serikyan leaves, you know?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.09,0:08:52.05,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,What are you saying...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.27,0:08:55.05,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Serika,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad I ran into you Nanami-chin!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.05,0:08:57.99,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Serika,0000,0000,0000,,Come to my concert!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.99,0:09:01.22,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Serika,0000,0000,0000,,I guess you can come, too, Hatate.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.61,0:09:03.12,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Serika,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.48,0:09:08.98,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Hatate Souta-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.39,0:09:11.28,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,What is it, Nanami-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.57,0:09:13.13,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,It could just be me,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.13,0:09:16.78,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,but I think I have an idea \Nwho this purple flag guy is.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.41,0:09:19.12,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,It's probably just you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.78,0:09:21.81,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I guess it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.81,0:09:23.58,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Silly me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.58,0:09:25.46,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Silly Nanami.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.17,0:09:29.89,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Is there anyone else who'd go off
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.89,0:09:32.29,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,about flags when no one wanted them to?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.29,0:09:34.19,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I had a lot of stuff
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.19,0:09:36.68,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,going on back then, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.05,0:09:39.36,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,When I saw her
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.63,0:09:43.18,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I was planning on taking
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.08,0:09:44.96,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,my own life.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.33,0:09:51.52,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I guess
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.21,0:09:54.88,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to do one good thing before I died.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.37,0:09:58.28,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Ultimately, I couldn't end it all, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.34,0:10:03.04,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,I guess it was pretty tough for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.26,0:10:06.85,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,So I wasn't really thinking \Nabout her specifically, per se.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.50,0:10:08.95,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I was just trying to make myself feel better.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.95,0:10:11.49,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, but you still helped her.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.49,0:10:13.41,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,You saved her, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.41,0:10:14.13,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.63,0:10:16.39,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Serikyan recovered,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.39,0:10:18.35,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,I got to know you...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.35,0:10:20.33,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone was happy in the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.70,0:10:24.53,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,You know, if you'd used your power like this from the start,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.53,0:10:26.02,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,you wouldn't have had such a hard time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.45,0:10:27.52,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Nanami...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.76,0:10:30.71,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, putting that aside...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.71,0:10:31.36,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.39,0:10:35.04,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,It pisses me off that Serikyan
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.04,0:10:37.53,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,owes you so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.48,0:10:37.53,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Wai—
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.53,0:10:40.47,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Making your way into \NSerikyan's heart like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.47,0:10:41.30,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,You're acting crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.60,0:10:42.93,Kanojo_Flag_Main,A,0000,0000,0000,,They're fighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.93,0:10:44.32,Kanojo_Flag_Main,B,0000,0000,0000,,First time I've seen something like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.28,0:10:54.38,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, it's time!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.67,0:10:56.91,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,It's finally the last day of the fair.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.91,0:11:00.30,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,It's time for the grand finale!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.67,0:11:02.80,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, the time has come!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.80,0:11:06.31,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Akane's got new clothes and \Ntotally is ready to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.57,0:11:09.37,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Way to go, Akane, but I've
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.37,0:11:12.75,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,mastered a new dance!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.75,0:11:15.36,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds like you're excited, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.66,0:11:17.80,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane(same),0000,0000,0000,,The night dance party!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.81,0:11:17.50,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Serikyan's concert!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.80,0:11:18.57,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.62,0:11:28.00,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Ta-da!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.25,0:11:32.75,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Sob. Sob.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.33,0:11:35.04,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,H-How are we, Souta?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.04,0:11:37.34,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,Don't just stand there. Say something.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.34,0:11:39.01,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Y-Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.72,0:11:44.18,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,You all look great.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.43,0:11:47.12,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, we all tried hard for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.12,0:11:49.19,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, we can't embarrass ourselves
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.19,0:11:51.35,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,when we dance with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.35,0:11:53.40,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? With me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.85,0:11:57.65,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kikuno,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone wants to dance with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.38,0:12:02.09,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Ruri,0000,0000,0000,,There's a legend regarding this dance party.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.09,0:12:03.16,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Legend?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.47,0:12:05.86,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Ruri,0000,0000,0000,,It'd be nice if the couples that
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.86,0:12:08.04,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Ruri,0000,0000,0000,,dance get married in the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.55,0:12:10.02,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Nice? That's all?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.02,0:12:13.12,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kurumiko,0000,0000,0000,,Must be nice to be a guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.12,0:12:16.67,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kurumiko,0000,0000,0000,,As your little sister, I don't \Nmind how many step-sisters I get.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.35,0:12:18.80,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kikuno,0000,0000,0000,,You can't say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.80,0:12:22.14,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kikuno,0000,0000,0000,,My little brother should \Nonly have one older sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.14,0:12:23.81,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,That doesn't even make any sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.09,0:12:26.96,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Tsumugi,0000,0000,0000,,It's nice being this old.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.96,0:12:28.60,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Tsumugi,0000,0000,0000,,I get to feel like I'm dancing with my grandson.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.85,0:12:31.01,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Mimori,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hatate-kun,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.01,0:12:34.56,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Mimori,0000,0000,0000,,could you dance with me, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.56,0:12:36.78,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I can't dance.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.78,0:12:39.61,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Hakua,0000,0000,0000,,I'll lead for you, I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.61,0:12:42.05,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Megumu,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone wants to dance with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.05,0:12:44.50,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone really wants to.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.50,0:12:46.70,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Will you dance with us?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.70,0:12:50.72,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Dance partner flags...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.37,0:12:53.57,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.57,0:12:54.96,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not confident at all,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.26,0:12:56.21,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,but let's dance.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.21,0:12:57.71,Kanojo_Flag_Main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.93,0:13:00.09,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,In that case it's a promise!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.09,0:13:01.91,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.17,0:13:10.43,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm fine with seeing Serikyan's \Nconcert alone, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.43,0:13:11.39,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.99,0:13:15.45,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,If you're the only one not dancing \Nit'll feel like you're left out,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.45,0:13:16.10,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.10,0:13:19.77,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,D-Don't say it before I do!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.38,0:13:45.63,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Serikyan!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.91,0:13:49.15,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Serika,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you all for coming to
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.15,0:13:50.89,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Serika,0000,0000,0000,,Serikyan's school concert!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.04,0:13:54.14,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Serika,0000,0000,0000,,Are you having fun at the fair?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.40,0:13:56.85,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Serika,0000,0000,0000,,I actually secretly went around
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.85,0:13:59.06,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Serika,0000,0000,0000,,the fair with some friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.06,0:14:00.89,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Serika,0000,0000,0000,,It was a lot of fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.89,0:14:03.65,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Serika,0000,0000,0000,,I totally love this school now!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.65,0:14:05.51,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Serikyan!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.43,0:14:09.81,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Serika,0000,0000,0000,,Today's concert will be broadcast
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.81,0:14:11.87,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Serika,0000,0000,0000,,to fans all around the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.87,0:14:15.41,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Serika,0000,0000,0000,,So cheer appropriately.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.54,0:14:20.84,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kikuno,0000,0000,0000,,Nanami-chan broke.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.84,0:14:23.61,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm kind of having fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.61,0:14:25.92,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,I want to shout with everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.19,0:14:28.14,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Broadcast all around the world. huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.14,0:14:29.43,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Pretty amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.36,0:14:32.94,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,She really made it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.47,0:14:35.03,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,She turned into a girl who inspires people,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.43,0:14:38.10,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,who represents their dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.98,0:14:40.60,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Serika,0000,0000,0000,,I found Nanami-chin.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.86,0:14:43.86,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Serika,0000,0000,0000,,I see that Hatate came, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.77,0:14:45.61,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Serika,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.08,0:14:53.78,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Serika,0000,0000,0000,,Listen to my song!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.04,0:14:58.44,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Serika,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}I saw you yesterday, \Nbut will I see you again today?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.44,0:15:02.60,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Serika,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}My biorhythm is focused on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.60,0:15:07.00,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Serika,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}We only could talk for a \Nbit, but I still got red.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.00,0:15:11.30,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Serika,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}I'm such a girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.30,0:15:13.10,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Serika,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}As the gelato melts,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.36,0:15:15.60,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Serika,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}as the candy melts...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.68,0:15:18.85,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.91,0:15:24.16,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,A flag of light?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.37,0:15:35.16,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Could this be...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.88,0:15:38.80,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Did my power get stronger when I met
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.03,0:15:41.85,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Serika, the bard?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.89,0:15:44.42,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,No, this light is...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.11,0:15:49.40,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,They're connected.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.70,0:15:53.22,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,The world is being drawn \Nto her flag and song.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.33,0:15:59.34,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,It's being drawn to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.39,0:16:08.00,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,So that's how it is..
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.03,0:16:11.82,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I thought that my death flag drew \Nevil from all over the world,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.38,0:16:15.95,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,and brought me nothing but despair.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.34,0:16:17.33,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,But that was wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.18,0:16:20.19,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I have people connected to me with
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.51,0:16:22.62,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,kindness that can overcome any evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.43,0:16:25.83,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I have people who give me hope \Nthat will paint over the despair.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.44,0:16:28.80,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,All I did was turn my back on the world,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.40,0:16:31.80,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,so I didn't notice something so simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.65,0:16:41.60,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Nanami...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.60,0:16:42.58,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Akane...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.88,0:16:43.56,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Okiku-nee...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.30,0:16:45.36,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.52,0:16:48.57,Kanojo_Flag_Main,No0,0000,0000,0000,,Hatate Souta.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.81,0:16:52.71,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,You're...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.80,0:16:55.41,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Number Zero.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.94,0:16:59.54,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,What are these numbers?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.18,0:17:03.38,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I guess other data than the \Nflags has become visible.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.84,0:17:07.45,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,The sudden growth of that power of \Nyours strained the servers,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.45,0:17:09.55,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,and the world froze.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.04,0:17:11.26,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,What are you saying—
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.05,0:17:14.99,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,The parallel world I went to with Mei.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.44,0:17:18.57,Kanojo_Flag_Main,No0,0000,0000,0000,,The term "virtual world" would be more apt.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.81,0:17:19.67,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Virtual?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.05,0:17:23.00,Kanojo_Flag_Main,No0,0000,0000,0000,,This is one of the many worlds we,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.00,0:17:24.85,Kanojo_Flag_Main,No0,0000,0000,0000,,the Council of the Seven Virtues,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.85,0:17:27.31,Kanojo_Flag_Main,No0,0000,0000,0000,,created to help combat the Angel Boat.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.97,0:17:29.78,Kanojo_Flag_Main,No0,0000,0000,0000,,An existence in the network.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.08,0:17:32.57,Kanojo_Flag_Main,No0,0000,0000,0000,,A world composed of data.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.82,0:17:36.65,Kanojo_Flag_Main,No0,0000,0000,0000,,The trouble began when
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.65,0:17:39.25,Kanojo_Flag_Main,No0,0000,0000,0000,,the system that exists in \Ncyberspace to watch over
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.25,0:17:41.84,Kanojo_Flag_Main,No0,0000,0000,0000,,the real world, the Angel \NBoat, went out of control.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.84,0:17:45.29,Kanojo_Flag_Main,No0,0000,0000,0000,,At this rate, it's only a matter \Nof time before humanity,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.29,0:17:47.83,Kanojo_Flag_Main,No0,0000,0000,0000,,which depends so much on the network, \Nis controlled by computers.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.31,0:17:50.32,Kanojo_Flag_Main,No0,0000,0000,0000,,In order to prevent that, we—
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.87,0:17:54.83,Kanojo_Flag_Main,No0,0000,0000,0000,,You seem rather calm.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.57,0:17:58.05,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to scream \Nand say you're lying,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.78,0:18:00.93,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,but the truth flag above your head,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.53,0:18:03.53,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,and everything I see here...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.85,0:18:07.38,Kanojo_Flag_Main,No0,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, your power is needed for the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.68,0:18:09.34,Kanojo_Flag_Main,No0,0000,0000,0000,,You can see the flags and control them.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.34,0:18:12.70,Kanojo_Flag_Main,No0,0000,0000,0000,,Only that power of yours that \Ncan alter the data of all events
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.70,0:18:16.02,Kanojo_Flag_Main,No0,0000,0000,0000,,can reach the Angel Boat in cyberspace.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.02,0:18:17.74,Kanojo_Flag_Main,No0,0000,0000,0000,,It is the best and only weapon we have.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.47,0:18:21.01,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I know,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.54,0:18:23.53,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,or more like I know everything now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.01,0:18:25.87,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I just gained all the
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.96,0:18:29.12,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,information on the network.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.36,0:18:34.32,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,But there is one thing I don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.82,0:18:36.13,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Why me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.54,0:18:38.35,Kanojo_Flag_Main,No0,0000,0000,0000,,We, the Council of the Seven Virtues,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.35,0:18:41.71,Kanojo_Flag_Main,No0,0000,0000,0000,,have been running simulations \Nin the worlds we created
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.71,0:18:43.65,Kanojo_Flag_Main,No0,0000,0000,0000,,with the data from all humanity.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.65,0:18:46.03,Kanojo_Flag_Main,No0,0000,0000,0000,,We set the simulations to run
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.27,0:18:48.44,Kanojo_Flag_Main,No0,0000,0000,0000,,one hundred million times
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.44,0:18:50.94,Kanojo_Flag_Main,No0,0000,0000,0000,,faster than reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.59,0:18:55.44,Kanojo_Flag_Main,No0,0000,0000,0000,,The Sacrament guided our way.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.79,0:18:58.38,Kanojo_Flag_Main,No0,0000,0000,0000,,You know the rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.04,0:19:01.10,Kanojo_Flag_Main,No0,0000,0000,0000,,The Hatate Souta of this world...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.40,0:19:03.92,Kanojo_Flag_Main,No0,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, only you have met with
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.92,0:19:05.74,Kanojo_Flag_Main,No0,0000,0000,0000,,the Sacrament and been given power.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.57,0:19:08.41,Kanojo_Flag_Main,No0,0000,0000,0000,,Is this a coincidence?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.41,0:19:10.73,Kanojo_Flag_Main,No0,0000,0000,0000,,Or an inevitability by the name of fate?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.73,0:19:12.56,Kanojo_Flag_Main,No0,0000,0000,0000,,That is up to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.03,0:19:15.29,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,What is Sakura...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.59,0:19:17.19,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,No, the Sacrament.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.57,0:19:19.12,Kanojo_Flag_Main,No0,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't really matter,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.42,0:19:21.38,Kanojo_Flag_Main,No0,0000,0000,0000,,now that your power has grown,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.38,0:19:23.70,Kanojo_Flag_Main,No0,0000,0000,0000,,and been perfected.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.34,0:19:26.20,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Sakura...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.45,0:19:30.24,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I understand everything now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.69,0:19:34.41,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Even I can't break this death flag of mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.79,0:19:35.77,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,It's a curse.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.48,0:19:38.67,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,You gave me this power
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.67,0:19:40.71,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,so I'd understand that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.20,0:19:44.47,Kanojo_Flag_Main,No0,0000,0000,0000,,Now, what will you do with \Nthat power, Hatate Souta?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.05,0:19:47.02,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,What will happen to this world now?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.58,0:19:49.90,Kanojo_Flag_Main,No0,0000,0000,0000,,Now that your power has been perfected,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.90,0:19:52.06,Kanojo_Flag_Main,No0,0000,0000,0000,,it won't end with a simple freeze next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.36,0:19:54.39,Kanojo_Flag_Main,No0,0000,0000,0000,,I imagine it'll completely collapse,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.22,0:19:57.31,Kanojo_Flag_Main,No0,0000,0000,0000,,so long as you are here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.56,0:19:59.56,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.49,0:20:04.80,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I... can't be here anymore, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.23,0:20:24.49,dance_party_20:18,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Dance Party
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.62,0:20:21.50,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Mimori,0000,0000,0000,,It's time for the Hatagaya \NSchool Fair to end!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.50,0:20:23.34,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Mimori,0000,0000,0000,,Good work, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.77,0:20:27.66,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Mimori,0000,0000,0000,,The only thing left is the dance party!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.66,0:20:29.08,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Mimori,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone dance
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.08,0:20:32.16,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Mimori,0000,0000,0000,,your hearts out!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.94,0:20:40.45,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,This is only one of the many virtual worlds.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.51,0:20:45.27,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,But... it was the only world I had.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.77,0:20:50.77,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,What is Souta off doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.77,0:20:52.22,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.22,0:20:56.02,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,He promised he'd dance with everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.27,0:20:59.03,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.70,0:21:01.66,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Nee-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.31,0:21:06.85,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,What was that feeling just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.15,0:21:09.84,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Is something wrong, Nanami-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.84,0:21:11.75,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.97,0:21:15.48,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Everything's going to be over soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.48,0:21:17.75,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what Souta's doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.25,0:21:21.38,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.26,0:21:25.34,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Who's Souta-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.67,0:21:27.32,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.42,0:23:12.66,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Roar! Gawo!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.03,0:23:15.45,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what I'm saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.13,0:23:19.39,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm thinking about that place, \Nall of them, before I realize it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.79,0:23:23.92,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure that's because \NI was happy until today.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.55,0:23:27.76,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I might not be able to go back.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.05,0:23:30.20,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,But as long as everyone's smiling back there,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.51,0:23:32.20,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,no matter what flags I have to break,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.01,0:23:35.01,Kanojo_Flag_Next_Ep_Number,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HF8979A&}Flag {\c&H3ADC97&}12
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.01,0:23:35.01,Kanojo_Flag_Next_Ep_Title,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,It's a {\c&HD8C46F&}Cruel World. {\c&HA257DA&}I'm Going to {\c&H65C798&}Take {\c&HD0CA62&}a Look in the Shadows.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.57,0:23:33.65,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I'll protect them.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.01,0:23:40.02,Kanojo_Show_Title_Small,,0000,0000,0000,,If {\c&H53AC43&}Her {\c&H085DF0&}Flag {\c&HD2C345&}Breaks
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.01,0:23:40.02,Kanojo_Flag_Watch,,0000,0000,0000,,You'd better watch next time!
